  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3189563/" class="title-link">白老虎的崛起</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3189563"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/MichelleHong/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1429348-317.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/MichelleHong/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Super小麦</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-04-22"
      class="main-meta">2010-04-22 15:58:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3189563_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我对印度是有特殊情感的，也不知道为什么。我在大学四年外加毕业闲适在家的一年里，独自背包去了5次印度。我能说简单的日常印地语，我亲密接触过印度社会的边缘受难者，我喜欢看一切印度人写的书和写印度的书，我对印度历史的了解远多于中国历史，我一直在努力学习印度文化相关...

